### Phase 5 — Scoping: Full Environment Hunt

Following initial findings, the hunt was expanded across the full estate using Falcon:

```sql
-- Hunt for malicious svchost copies outside System32
event_simpleName=ProcessRollup2
| search FileName="svchost.exe"
  AND NOT FilePath="C:\\Windows\\System32\\"
  AND NOT FilePath="C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\"
| stats count by ComputerName, FilePath, SHA256HashData
```

**Results:**
```
MFG-WS-031   C:\Windows\Temp\svchost.exe      SHA256: 7f83b1...
MFG-WS-047   C:\Windows\Temp\svchost.exe      SHA256: 7f83b1...  (same hash)
MFG-SRV-003  C:\ProgramData\Microsoft\svchost.exe  SHA256: 7f83b1...
MFG-SRV-007  C:\Windows\Temp\svchost.exe      SHA256: 7f83b1...
```

4 compromised hosts. All running the same implant. All missed by automated detection for 47 days.

