## Containment Actions

1. Removed WMI subscriptions from all 4 hosts via CrowdStrike RTR
2. Deleted malicious `svchost.exe` copies from all affected paths
3. Blocked `94.102.49.190` at perimeter firewall
4. Invalidated `svc_mfg_automation` Kerberos tickets — forced re-authentication
5. Deployed Falcon Custom IOA rule for WMI EventConsumer creation
6. Deployed Zeek beacon detection script across all network segments

